Soul's Desire is a gate-town in Mount Celestia whose portal leads to Bytopia. It is located on the shore of the Silver Sea in Lunia, on the same mountain-island as Heart's Faith.
Celestia's portals resemble large blocks of finished stones. White granite stones shot with silver leads to Bytopia. 

